snippet.title: Happy's Humble Burger Farm - Launch | PS5, PS4
snippet.description: Congratulations, you’ve just been hired to work the night shift! Grill patties, operate deep fryers, pour drinks and serve customers... but whatever you do, don't make Happy angry. Happy's Humble Burger Farm, a first person adventure horror cooking game, is coming to PlayStation on December 3rd!
